      <title>据彭博社报道，瑞银考虑与北京政府进行瑞信中国股权互换</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/ubs-weighs-credit-suisse-china-stake-swap-with-beijing-government-bloomberg-news-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社周一报道，瑞银正在洽谈通过将其在瑞士信贷旗下境内证券公司的股份与北京政府投资基金进行互换，获得其中国平台的全部所有权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/ubs-weighs-credit-suisse-china-stake-swap-with-beijing-government-bloomberg-news-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 00:54:40 GMT</pubDate>
